Package travelAgencyModel

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Address
    Simple implementation of an address Implements Serializable
    Bus
    Class containing the most basic information about a bus, such as make, model, license plate and passenger capacity.
    BusAndChaffeurTravel
    Extension of Travel that forces a single Chauffeur and a personCount to be included.
    BusList
    ArrayList backed list containing instances of Bus.
    Chauffeur
    Chauffeur class containing basic information about a chauffeur, such as name, an ID, phone number, email and address.
    ChauffeurList
    ArrayList backed list containing instances of Chauffeur.
    Customer
    Customer class containing basic information about a customer such as name and phone number.
    CustomerList
    ArrayList backed list containing instances of Customer.
    DestinationsList
    ArrayList backed list containing instances of String.
    Passenger
    Passenger class containing basic information about a passenger, such as name, phone number and birthday.
    PassengerList
    ArrayList backed list containing instances of Passenger and Tickets.
    Program  
    Ticket
    Ticket class which stores a ticket price and the Passenger owner of the ticket.
    Time
    Abstract time class that proves some helper methods
    Tour
    Extension of Travel that adds departure, arrival and return dates as well as a CustomerList to keep track of the Customers associated with this Tour.
    Travel
    Abstract class Travel generalizes a Tour and BusAndChauffeurTravel.
    TravelAgency
    Gateway class for the underlying model.
    TravelsList
    ArrayList backed list containing instances of classes extending Travel
